                  <T>0x724D8582<!--String: "If you've got an excess of any berry but find yourself in need of another, I hear the Creature Keeper's the one to see for a helpful berry trade."--></T>
                  <T>0xA15434D2<!--String: "Chocoberries can be hard to find. That's common knowledge. What they don't know is that there are some growing on the Isle of Volpe in the Bramblewood. Shhhh. Don't tell anyone!"--></T>
